{
  "stem": "4032.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "After being there for, like, four months, five months, the Russians wanted all the people, all the refugees, that was like a-- they were calling that the borderline, because I don't know if they expected the Germans to attack Russia at that time, but that was 1940.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the-- the Germans attacked Russia in 1941.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But by that time, I was already in Siberia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They came one morning to the door and knocked on the door.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They knew-- I don't know how they know, but they knew that somebody lives here which is a refugee.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they knocked on the door, and they asked me my name.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I stated my name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I-- he says, come to the office of the NKVD.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It's the secret police.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we'll question you, and we'll let you go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I said, let me take a few things with me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He says, no, you don't have to.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You'll be, after three, four hours, released.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That was not true.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "When they arrested us, they put us in trains, cattle trains, and sent us to Siberia.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That was June, 1940.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they sent us to Siberia, and we started to work there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I was young, and I did work very hard in order to-- because the Russian system says if you work, they call it [RUSSIAN], a-- something that you specialize in more and-- and better work.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we-- we were a group of 10.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were cutting trees in the woods.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we worked very hard, and the-- and there was a [RUSSIAN] that they gave.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A-- you have to do so much.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "By 12 o'clock, we're through doing so much, so whatever we did from 12:00 to 3:00 or to 4:00, because-- so we got the extra piece of bread, extra cigarette.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
